name: SPIROFLOGO
description:
Spiroflogo is fun but above all very decorative, and super zen on top of that.
It is an endless digital spectrum loop made up of pixels and animated in vintage ways. A pure post-millennium lo-fi cryptocanvas.
It remains simple and discreet on a daily basis but its psy / chic aspect is perfectly suited for a reception, or a more trendy atmosphere.
Your friends will love it.
